            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Environment</b> any land<br/><b>Organization</b> solitary, guard (2\u20134 plus 2\u20134 ghouls), or pack (4\u20136 plus 2\u20134 ghouls)<br/><b>Treasure</b> none"
